Release details, version LTS.405
Patch LTS.405.3 of March 29, 2024
Changes and improvements
Working with styles for the
Title by attribute
widget was stabilized
Patch LTS.405.2
Changes and improvements
Access permissions when working with objects were stabilized
Edoc: document version comparison was stabilized
Patch LTS.405.1
Changes and improvements
Minor changes and improvements.
Update package LTS.405.0 of March 26, 2024
New features
Functionality for analyzing effective permissions by object was added.
The possibility to switch to editing of the business process flowchart directly from the route object flowchart was added.
The possibility of creating new SQL-based data sources can be managed in the configuration file.
New Edoc functionality: it is now possible to switch from a bookmark to a questionnaire item and to attach a document in a user-defined format. The name of the downloaded document can now be specified by the algorithm.
Changes and improvements
Generating an object data source was optimized;
Visuals of objects when working with business processes were optimized;
Working with objects in Text Message widget was stabilized;
Working with the multiselect attribute when creating a new instance was stabilized;
Working with reporting forms was stabilized;
Working with algorithm compilation was stabilized;
Display of drop-down lists in the System was stabilized;
Working with the Theme Designer when copying themes was stabilized;
Working with GUF files was stabilized;
Working with subject area objects was stabilized;
Working with the registry: display of data in columns was stabilized;
Working with the dashboard visual was stabilized;
Edoc: Text editing functionality in the Edoc editor was improved. Settings for creating and attaching a file, downloading a file in the working with bookmarks mode were improved. Display of buttons when working with Edoc was optimized;
Display of unread chats in GreenData Desktop Messenger was stabilized;
System performance was improved.
